CGI-Application-Plugin-Config-IniFiles version 0.02
===================================================

This little plugin makes it a little more comfortable to use
Config::IniFiles in your scripts using CGI::Application.

Version 0.02 supports passing Config::IniFiles objects instead
of filenames.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  CGI::Application
  Config::IniFiles

